---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Increased to accommodate descriptions */
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        li:before {
            content: '‚Ä¢';
            color: #007BFF; /* Change to your preferred bullet color */
            font-size: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .description {
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-left: 20px; /* Aligns with bullet text */
        }
        code {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 2px 4px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF; /* Match bullet color for consistency */
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
		.billboard {
			background-color: #900C3F; /* Vibrant background color */
			padding: 16px;
			border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners for the billboard */
			box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Shadow for depth */
			text-align: center;
			position: relative;
			margin: 20px auto; /* Center the billboard */
			max-width: 80%; /* Adjust based on your preference */
}

		.marquee-container {
			padding: 10px;
			background-color: #FF5733; /* Bright background for the text area */
			border-radius: 5px; /* Slightly rounded corners within the billboard */
		}

		.marquee-text {
			font-size: 24px;
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #FFFFFF; /* Bright text for visibility */
			font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; /* Choose a bold, clear font */
		}

		.lights-top, .lights-bottom {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			left: 0;
			right: 0;
			height: 10px;
			background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #FFFF33, #FFFF33 10px, transparent 10px, transparent 20px); /* Simulating lights */
		}

		.lights-top {
			top: 0;
			border-top-left-radius: 10px;
			border-top-right-radius: 10px;
		}

		.lights-bottom {
			bottom: 0;
			border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
			border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
		}

				.highlighted {
					background-color: #f5deb3; /* Highlight background */
					color: black; /* Text color */
					padding: 5px; /* Some padding around the text */
					border-radius: 5px; /* Optional: rounded corners */
		}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
    <main>
		<div class="billboard">
			<div class="lights-top"></div>
			<div class="marquee-container">
				<marquee class="marquee-text">üåê Web. üìä Analytics. üé∫ Music. üè¨ Markets. ü§ñ Flexwork. </marquee>
			</div>
			<div class="lights-bottom"></div>
		</div>
		
				<h1>üßëüèª‚Äçüíª Chris Blogs</h1>
		<p>Hey there, I'm Chris Rotunno, and you've landed on "Chris Blogs", my personal platform for <span class="highlighted">development</span>, <span class="highlighted">discovery</span>, and <span class="highlighted">content creation</span>.
			My interests are multifaceted and range from cat humor to entropy. Arranged in no partcular order, here are some of the topics touched on in this blog:</p>
        <ul>
			<li><h4>Web Development</h4>
                <div class="description">Delving into the digital realm, one line of code at a time, crafting seamless experiences.</div>
            </li>
            <li><h4>Data Analytics</h4>
                <div class="description">Harnessing the power of data to uncover actionable insights and inform decision-making.</div>
            </li>
            <li><h4>Music Industry</h4>
                <div class="description">Exploring the vibrant world of music through artists, emerging trends, and cultural shifts.</div>
            </li>
			<li><h4>Financial Markets</h4>
                <div class="description">Navigating the intricacies of trading, from traditional stock exchanges to the dynamic sphere of decentralized platforms.</div>
            </li>
            <li><h4>Post-COVID Workplace</h4>
                <div class="description">Exploring the evolution of flexible working in remote environments, reduced hours, and improved work-life balance.</div>
            </li>
        </ul>        <!-- Additional content and helpful links -->
    </main>
    <Footer />
</body>
</html>
